Listed by @3SAEstate for 4,900,000 € 🔑
This modern villa offers a total of seven bedroom suites and is a fantastic house for families and visitors, suited for the lifestyle in Marbella. ☀️ This home is functional, modern, and state-of-the-art, with modern equipment and technologies. 🌴

Property details:
✔️ Surface 842 M²
✔️ Plot 1360 M²
✔️ 7 Bedrooms
✔️ 7 Bathrooms
✔️ Panoramic golf & sea views
✔️ Swimming pool
✔️ Mancave with bar
✔️ Playroom

📍 La Alquería

Contact @3SAEstate for more information! 🔑
-

node.text:
Listed by @PaulBensonev 🔑
This mountain contemporary family home in Deer Valley! Located in the exclusive Hidden Meadows neighborhood offering unparalleled privacy while capturing panoramic ski resort and mountain views. ⛰️ Ideal floor plan to entertain family and friends featuring a gourmet kitchen, indoor and outdoor dining spaces, a second family/multimedia room, a grand primary suite with vaulted ceilings and a fireplace, a private floor for guests, and an executive office with mountain views. 😍 Enjoy wildlife viewing amid the luxury of a 1.75-acre lot with more than 6 acres of open space immediately adjacent to your property. ✨
-

#Parkcity #Luxuryhome #design #Utah #realestate #mansion #home #luxuryrealestate #property #realtor #parkcityrealestate #listed

These new luxury homes in Nueva Andalucia are part of a new development that offers three different types of modern villas. 😍

The villas are newly built to the highest of standards, with widen open-plan living spaces and stunning finishes. They are designed to mix luxury and nature in a spectacular setting. 🤍

📍 Marbella

Property details:
- Surface 658 - 684M²⁠⠀⁠
- Plot 1,008 - 1,135M²⠀
- 4 Bedrooms⁠⠀
- ⁠Mountain views
- Swimming pool
- Chill-out area
- Fireplace

Asking price 1,895,000€

Contact @3SAEstate for more information! 🔑
